Jeremy

----- Original Message ----
From: Wes Kellington &lt;kq4ok@...&gt;
To: EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com
Sent: Thursday, April 24, 2008 9:45:25 AM
Subject: [EVP-ITC] This is my second post





Hi, my name is Wes 
Kellington, and I am from Waynesboro, VA.  This is my second post since 
joining the group
on March 
1.

I came here 
specifically to listen and learn from Frank Sumption and to likeminded 
individuals.  I am a ham radio operator,
although I have not 
been active in years since the CB&#39;ers kind of took over with their new no-code 
rules, and am a 
computer 
technician.  I have been passionately pursuing paranormal interests since I 
was a child.  So, Frank, please
keep on supplying us 
with your knowledge and foresight.  I look forward to your posts; and I 
read all of them.

I read all the 
posts, even by the guy with the gall to ask for someone to send him a 
radio.  Yes, I would give anything
to have one; but I 
would not dare ask someone to do that for me.  That&#39;s just wrong!  And 
as far as threatening
personal emails, 
what the Hell has been the matter with people?  My wife is the business 
manager of a local 
psychiatric 
practice.  The day of the full moon, they had more patients and admitted 
more people to the psychiatric
wing of the hospital 
than ever!

This is 
off-topic.  I have been dealing with a personal problem for the past 
several weeks.  I had a chest X-ray; and
on it they found a 
2.5 cm nodule in one of my lungs.  My catscan is May 8th to make sure I do 
not have lung cancer.
The waiting is 
killing me.  It&#39;s like being on death row and waiting to see if the phone 
rings.  So, I have not had the
energy to do 
anything lately.  I am only waiting...

Hopefully, there 
will be a positive outcome, and then I can delve into this further and begin 
some research of my own.

Frank, please stick 
around.

Wes


